Package: FOCuS
Type: Package
Title: Fast Online Changepoint Detection via Functional Pruning CUSUM statistics
Version: 1.4.1
Date: 2021-10-10
Authors@R: c(person("Gaetano", "Romano", email = "g.romano@lancaster.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Idris", "Eckley", role = c("aut")), person("Paul", "Fearnhead", role = c("aut")), person("Guillem", "Rigaill", role = c("aut", "ctb")))
Maintainer: Gaetano Romano <g.romano@lancaster.ac.uk>
Description: FOCuS is a package for detecting changes in mean in real-time in an univariate sequence in real time. This is achieved via an exact optimization of a sequential CUSUM statistics. 
